<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" style="font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif">
<head> 
  <meta charset="UTF-8"> 
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport"> 
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"> 
  <title>Poetica Activation Email</title> 
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dddddd;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #333333;
    }
    .content {
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .content h3 {
        margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #333333;
    }
    .content p {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555555;
    }
    .content .activation-code {
        display: block;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #333333;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #888888;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer a {
        color: #007BFF;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Poetica</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for registering with Poetica. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
            <span class="activation-code"><%= activation %></span>
            <p>Please enter this code on the verification page to complete your registration.</p>
            <p>If you did not register for a Poetica account, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@poetica.com">support@poetica.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
